history.content:
I'm a sophomore and will be declaring CS at the end of this semester and the only lower divs I have left are 16b and 61c. However, I want to take an upper div, probably 170, next semester and push 61c to next year. Since it is not guaranteed that I’ll be able to get into an upper div from the waitlist, though, I thought about adding 61c in phase 2 just in case. I was wondering if that would be safe as I don’t want to end up with just 16b in the end. I have to phase 1 another class as well, so can’t add both 61c and upper div in phase 1 along with 16b. 

Also, how likely would I be to get into 170, or another upper div if I have a better chance, from the waitlist if I phase 1? Thanks!
history.subject: CS61C in Phase 2
